Various Ubuntu settings.

* ibus-setup:  Run "ibus-setup" in the terminal and set the "Emoji" shortcut to
  something else, because otherwise Ctrl-; keeps popping up an "e" tooltip.

* To get dark mode in Firefox PDF display:  Create file ~/snap/firefox/common/.mozilla/firefox/*.default/chrome/userContent.css with content:

#viewerContainer > #viewer > .page > .canvasWrapper > canvas {
   filter: invert(70%);
}

* Increase mouse pointer size:  Start "dconf-editor", go to
  org/gnome/desktop/interface/cursor-size and change the value.
  
